dc_title_s: Map of Michigan; published by S. Wangersheim.
dc_description_s: Shows county and township boundaries. Includes continuation inset of upper peninsula. Pp. 64-65 from an atlas. 1 map: col.; 63 x 40 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
